           <ab>
              <lb n="1"/>
               <expan>
                  <abbr>D</abbr>
                  <ex>is</ex>
               </expan>
               <persName>Faustina</persName>
               <expan>
                  <abbr>M</abbr>
                  <ex>anibus</ex>
               </expan>
              <lb n="2"/>
              <choice><reg>coniugi</reg><orig>coiugi</orig></choice>
               suo dulcissimo
              <lb n="3"/><persName key="Primitivus" type="cognomen"><choice><reg>Primitivo</reg><orig>Primitibo</orig></choice></persName>bene merenti<add place="right">qui <abbr>f</abbr> ano</add>
              <lb n="4"/>
               <add place="left"><num value="40"/>XL</num></add>
               qum quo<note>sic</note> vixit annis
               <num value="12"/>XII</num> annis
               <expan><abbr>me</abbr><ex>n</ex>s<ex>ibus</ex>
               </expan>
              <lb n="5"/><num value="8"/>VIII</num>diebus<num value="7"/>VII</num>et discentes
              <lb n="6"/>fecerunt<persName>Felix</persName>et<persName type="attested">Maximi</persName>
              <lb break="no">
              <lb n="7"/>nus magistro bene merenti</lb>
            </ab>
         </div>
         <div type="apparatus">
            <app loc="147">
               <note>Both Primitibus and Primitivus are cognomena attested to previously (see CIL #s) but sometimes is noted as a error by the workman<note></note></note>
            </app>
            <app loc="150">
               <note>Here the craftsman likely meant cumquo instead of the uncommon qumquo.</note>
            </app>
         </div>
         <!---marked by line number? Editor's notes (non corrections) here? --->
         <div type="translation" xml:lang="en">
            <p>To the Shades of the Underworld. Faustina (made this) for her most dear and well-deserving husband Primiti[v]us, who was in his forieth year of life (?), with whom she lived twelve years , eight months, seven days; and also Felix and Maximinus, students (?), made this for their well-deserving teacher.</p>
            <ab/></ab>
         </div>
